{
  "texts": [
    "It is generally believed that with thorough professional development support, teachers play a crucial role in professional growth and are critical to successfully integrating STEM into schools (Geng et al. 2019).",
    "Research Gap.",
    "Despite significant initiatives like the \"13th Five-Year Plan\" and the \"China STEM Education 2029 Innovation Action Plan,\" there is a notable lack of research examining the specific objectives, methodologies, and outcomes of STEM TPD programs in China.",
    "No comprehensive review has yet analyzed the existing literature to understand the current state of TPD and its role in implementing China's national STEM education goals.",
    "This knowledge gap limits the ability to draw meaningful lessons, identify trends, or improve upon these initiatives."
  ]
}